/** * Computes the set of possible outcomes of the {@code ToBoolean} predicate * for this type. The {@code ToBoolean} predicate is defined by the ECMA-262 * standard, 3rd edition. Its behavior for simple types can be * summarized by the following table: * * * * * * * * *
typeresult
{@code undefined}{false}
{@code null}{false}
{@code boolean}{true, false}
{@code number}{true, false}
{@code string}{true, false}
{@code Object}{true}
* @return the set of boolean literals for this type */
